                    <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
                        Forming a <strong>UK Ltd company from Pakistan for e-commerce</strong> is one of the most powerful moves a Pakistani entrepreneur can make. A UK Limited Company unlocks Amazon UK, Shopify Payments, Stripe, and global PayPal — payment gateways that reject Pakistan-registered entities outright.
                    </p>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
                        You do not need to visit the UK. You do not need a UK bank account before you start. The entire process is completed online in as little as 24 hours. Here is exactly how to do it:
                    </p>

                    <ol class="space-y-5 mb-8">
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
                            <span class="w-8 h-8 bg-brand-blue text-white rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center font-black text-sm shrink-0 mt-0.5">1</span>
                            <div>
                                <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-1">Choose a unique company name</h4>
                                <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">Your company name must end in "Limited" or "Ltd" and cannot match any existing name on the Companies House register. Use our free name checker to verify availability instantly before you apply.</p>
                            </div>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
                            <span class="w-8 h-8 bg-brand-blue text-white rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center font-black text-sm shrink-0 mt-0.5">2</span>
                            <div>
                                <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-1">Select the right e-commerce SIC codes</h4>
                                <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">For online retail, use SIC 47910 (Retail via mail order or internet). Add 47990 for Amazon FBA marketplace sales. Correct SIC codes significantly improve your business bank account approval rate with Wise and Tide.</p>
                            </div>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
                            <span class="w-8 h-8 bg-brand-blue text-white rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center font-black text-sm shrink-0 mt-0.5">3</span>
                            <div>
                                <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-1">Register with a London registered office address</h4>
                                <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">As a Pakistani national, your UK Ltd requires a physical UK registered office address. Our Standard Plus and Enterprise packages include a prestigious London W1 address — keeping your home address completely off the public Companies House record.</p>
                            </div>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
                            <span class="w-8 h-8 bg-brand-blue text-white rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center font-black text-sm shrink-0 mt-0.5">4</span>
                            <div>
                                <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-1">Pass ACSP identity verification</h4>
                                <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">Under the 2024 ECCTA rules, all UK company formations now require identity verification through an Authorised Corporate Service Provider (ACSP). We handle this digitally — no in-person appointment, no embassy visit. Just upload your passport and we file everything on your behalf.</p>
                            </div>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
                            <span class="w-8 h-8 bg-brand-blue text-white rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center font-black text-sm shrink-0 mt-0.5">5</span>
                            <div>
                                <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-1">Open a Wise Business account</h4>
                                <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">Wise Business is the top choice for Pakistani e-commerce founders. It accepts UK Ltd owners of any nationality, provides GBP, USD, EUR, and PKR accounts with no minimum deposit, and integrates directly with Amazon Seller Central, Shopify, and Stripe. Funds arrive in your Pakistani bank account with fees as low as 0.4%.</p>
                            </div>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
                            <span class="w-8 h-8 bg-brand-blue text-white rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center font-black text-sm shrink-0 mt-0.5">6</span>
                            <div>
                                <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-1">Register on Amazon UK, EU & Shopify</h4>
                                <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">With your UK Ltd Companies House number, HMRC UTR, and Wise bank account details, you can register on Amazon UK Seller Central within days. Your products qualify for Prime, FBA UK/EU warehouses, and the pan-European marketplace covering 27 countries — all from Lahore, Karachi, or Islamabad.</p>
                            </div>
                        </li>
                    </ol>

